'''努诺·亚历山大·塔瓦雷斯·门德斯'''（{{lang-pt|Nuno Alexandre Tavares Mendes}}；{{bd|2002年|6月19日}}），是一名葡萄牙足球运动员，场上司职[[后卫_(足球)|左后卫]]，現時由[[葡萄牙足球超级联赛|葡超]]球队[[葡萄牙体育俱乐部|葡萄牙体育]]租借至[[法国足球甲级联赛|法甲]]球队[[巴黎圣日耳曼足球俱乐部|巴黎圣日耳曼]]，亦是[[葡萄牙国家足球队|葡萄牙国家队]]队员之一。

==俱乐部生涯==
努诺·门德斯于2002年6月19日出生在[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[里斯本大区|里斯本大区]]的[[辛特拉|辛特拉镇]]，他是安哥拉裔。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sporting/detalhe/nuno-mendes-o-meu-pai-estaria-orgulhoso-de-mim|title=Nuno Mendes: "O meu pai estaria orgulhoso de mim"|trans-title=Nuno Mendes: "My father would be proud of me"|newspaper=《{{le|记录报|Record (newspaper)}}》|first=Ricardo|last=Granada|language=pt|date=2020-07-31|access-date=2020-11-26}}</ref>努诺·门德斯在10岁就加入了[[葡萄牙体育俱乐部|葡萄牙体育]]的青训学院。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://oambidestro.pt/2020/05/19/nuno-mendes-o-futuro-dono-da-lateral-esquerda-dos-leoes/|title=Nuno Mendes, o futuro dono da lateral esquerda dos leões|trans-title=Nuno Mendes, the future owner of the Lions' left-back berth|publisher=O Ambidestro|first=Alexandre|last=Ribeiro|language=pt|date=2020-05-19|access-date=2020-06-12}}</ref>2020年6月12日，在葡萄牙体育主场1-0战胜[[费雷拉足球俱乐部|费雷拉]]的[[葡萄牙足球超级联赛|葡超]]比赛中的第72分钟{{le|替补 (足球)|Substitute (association football)|替补}}出场，换下了阿根廷后卫{{le|马科斯·阿库尼亚|Marcos Acuña|阿库尼亚}}，完成了一线队首秀。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sporting/detalhe/sporting-bate-pacos-de-ferreira-com-grande-golo-de-jovane|title=Sporting bate Paços de Ferreira com grande golo de Jovane|trans-title=Sporting beat Paços de Ferreira with great Jovane goal|newspaper=《{{le|记录报|Record (newspaper)}}》|language=pt|date=2020-06-12|access-date=2020-11-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sporting/detalhe/nuno-mendes-estreou-se-aos-17-anos-pela-equipa-principal-do-sporting|title=Nuno Mendes estreou-se aos 17 anos pela equipa principal do Sporting|trans-title=Nuno Mendes made debut for Sporting's first team aged 17|newspaper=《{{le|记录报|Record (newspaper)}}》|language=pt|date=2020-06-12|access-date=2020-06-26}}</ref> 

在2020赛季开始前，阿库尼亚离开了葡萄牙体育，加盟了[[西班牙足球甲级联赛|西甲]]球队[[塞维利亚足球俱乐部|塞维利亚]]。这也使得努诺·门德斯成为了球队主帅{{le|鲁本·阿莫里姆|Rúben Amorim|阿莫里姆}}在左后卫位置上的首选，而他在此时年仅18岁。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/1a-liga/sporting/noticias/dois-tubaroes-perguntaram-por-nuno-mendes-eis-a-resposta-do-sporting-12698124.html|title=Dois "tubarões" perguntaram por Nuno Mendes: eis a resposta do Sporting|trans-title=Two "sharks" asked about Nuno Mendes: here's what Sporting replied|newspaper=《{{le|比赛报|O Jogo}}》|first1=Duarte|last1=Tornesi|first2=Rui Miguel|last2=Gomes|language=pt|date=2020-09-07|access-date=2020-11-12}}</ref>同年10月4日，在葡萄牙体育2-0客胜[[波蒂莫嫩塞竞技俱乐部|波尔蒂芒人]]的比赛中，努诺·门德斯打进一球，这也是他在正式比赛中为葡萄牙体育打进的第一粒进球。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://observador.pt/2020/10/04/nuno-mendes-nao-desiste-por-ele-e-pelo-clube-a-cronica-do-portimonense-sporting/|title=Nuno Mendes não desiste. Por ele e pelo clube (a crónica do Portimonense-Sporting)|trans-title=Nuno Mendes does not quit. For him and for club (Portimonense-Sporting match report)|newspaper=《{{le|观察者报|Observador}}》|first=Bruno|last=Roseiro|language=pt|date=2020-10-04|access-date=2020-11-11}}</ref>

2020年12月19日，努诺·门德斯与葡萄牙体育续约至2025年，同时也将他的{{le|买断条款|buyout clause|违约金}}从4500万欧元提高到了7000万欧元。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://onefootball.com/en/news/inter-linked-nuno-mendes-extends-contract-with-sporting-lisbon-portuguese-media-report-32001816|title=Inter linked Nuno Mendes extends contract with Sporting Lisbon, Portuguese media report|publisher=OneFootball|date=2020-12-19|access-date=2020-12-22}}</ref>

2021年8月31日，努诺·门德斯以租借方式加盟巴黎圣日耳曼，租借期为一个赛季，巴黎圣日耳曼有购入的選項。

==国家队生涯==
2020年9月4日，在刚完成了俱乐部首秀后，努诺·门德斯在[[葡萄牙21岁以下国家足球队|葡萄牙U-21国家队]]4-0完胜[[塞浦路斯21岁以下国家足球队|塞浦路斯U-21国家队]]的[[欧洲U-21足球锦标赛|U-21欧洲杯]]{{le|2021年欧洲U-21足球锦标赛预选赛|2021 UEFA European Under-21 Championship qualification|预选赛}}中完成了他的U-21[[葡萄牙国家足球队|国家队]]{{le|出场 (体育)|Cap (sport)|首秀}}。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://ominho.pt/rui-jorge-estreia-tres-jogadores-do-sporting-e-um-do-benfica-nos-sub-21/|title=Rui Jorge estreia três jogadores do Sporting e um do Benfica nos sub-21|trans-title=Rui Jorge gives debut to three Sporting players and one from Benfica in under-21s|newspaper=O Minho|language=pt|date=2020-08-24|access-date=2020-11-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://maisfutebol.iol.pt/selecao-nacional/portugal-sub21/sub21-portugal-goleia-em-chipre-e-diogo-leite-bisa|title=Sub21: Portugal goleia em Chipre e Diogo Leite bisa|trans-title=Under21: Portugal rout in Cyprus and Diogo Leite grabs brace|publisher=Mais Futebol|language=pt|date=2020-09-04|access-date=2020-11-12}}</ref>6个月后，努诺·门德斯在葡萄牙1-0小胜[[阿塞拜疆国家足球队|阿塞拜疆]]的[[2022年国际足联世界杯|2022年]][[国际足联世界杯|世界杯]][[2022年国际足协世界杯外围赛_(欧洲区)|预选赛]]中首发出战，并打满了全场比赛，完成了成年国家队首秀。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://portugoal.net/selecao/2008-sporting-duo-nuno-mendes-and-joao-palhinha-called-into-portugal-squad-as-cedric-earns-recall|title=Sporting duo Nuno Mendes and João Palhinha called into Portugal squad as Cédric earns recall|publisher=PortuGOAL|first=Tom|last=Kundert|date=2021-03-16|access-date=2021-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://portugoal.net/selecao/2025-portugal-beat-azerbaijan-1-0-in-opening-world-cup-qualifier|title=Portugal beat Azerbaijan 1–0 in opening World Cup qualifier|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=2021-03-24|access-date=2021-03-24}}</ref>

